flowchart TD
    %% External Entities
    C[/Candidate/]
    G[/Google Gemini API/]
    A[/AssemblyAI\nStreaming WS/]
    V[/VAPI TTS/]

    %% Data Stores
    D1[(D1: users\ncollection)]
    D2[(D2: interview_runs\ncollection)]
    D3[(D3: Flask\nSession)]

    %% Processes
    P1((1.0\nAuthenticate\nUser))
    P2((2.0\nParse Resume\n& Extract Skills))
    P3((3.0\nGenerate\nQuestions))
    P4((4.0\nDeliver Question\nvia TTS))
    P5((5.0\nStream &\nTranscribe Audio))
    P6((6.0\nEvaluate\nAnswer))
    P7((7.0\nCompute Final\nScore & Report))

    %% Auth flow
    C -->|Register / Login credentials| P1
    P1 <-->|Verify / Store user| D1
    P1 -->|Authenticated session| C

    %% Resume flow
    C -->|PDF resume upload| P2
    P2 -->|Weighted skill profile| D3
    P2 -->|Skill profile| P3

    %% Question generation
    P3 <-->|Skill-aware prompt / Questions JSON| G
    P3 -->|5 personalised questions| D3

    %% Interview loop
    D3 -->|Next question text| P4
    P4 <-->|Text to Audio URL| V
    P4 -->|Question audio| C

    C -->|Microphone PCM16 stream| P5
    P5 <-->|Audio frames / Live transcript| A
    P5 -->|Transcript + typed answer| P6

    %% Evaluation
    P6 <-->|Answer + rubric prompt / Scores JSON| G
    P6 -->|Per-question score| D3
    D3 -->|Accumulated scores| P7

    %% Final report
    P7 -->|Final evaluation & hire verdict| D2
    P7 -->|Results page data| C

    %% Styling
    style C fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb
    style G fill:#fef9c3,stroke:#ca8a04
    style A fill:#fef9c3,stroke:#ca8a04
    style V fill:#fef9c3,stroke:#ca8a04
    style D1 fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#16a34a
    style D2 fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#16a34a
    style D3 fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#16a34a
